<h2><strong><img role="presentation" src="https://canvas.tccd.edu/courses/53595/files/6621160/preview" alt="" width="50" height="50" data-api-endpoint="https://canvas.tccd.edu/api/v1/courses/53595/files/6621160" data-api-returntype="File" />&nbsp;Discussion Question/Prompt</strong></h2>
<p><span>Please tell me about yourself in a short post (250-300 words). Include your name.</span></p>
<ul>
    <li><span>Tell what your reason for taking this course.</span></li>
    <li><span>Share one thing that you hope to learn this semester.</span></li>
    <li><span>Share one activity or pastime that you pursue when you are not in school.</span></li>
    <li><span>If you would like to include information about your family, your work or career, or your life outside of the classroom, please share (school appropriate please).&nbsp;</span></li>
    <li><span>Photographs or videos are also welcome (school appropriate please).</span></li>
</ul>
